Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBallCmd
    This abstract interface is used to send commands to balls.
    IModel2ViewAdapter
    This is an interface which defines the functions that the model wants the view to have/do.
    IPaintStrategy
    This is an interface for an IPaintStrategy that defines the methods we want it to have.
    IShapeFactory
    This interface defines the methods we want a shape factory to have.
    IStrategyFac
    This interface defines the functions we want IStrategyFac to have.
    IUpdateStrategy
    This interface defines the functions we want IUpdateStrategies to have.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APaintStrategy
    This is an abstract class that defines the top level affine transform based paint strategy.
    Ball
    This is the Ball class, which is what is drawn on the screen, and implements Observer to use dispatching.
    BallPaintStrategy
    This is the ball paint strategy, which implements a paint strategy for a ball.
    BallWorldModel
    This is the BallWorldModel class, which makes balls, clears balls, and updates the balls.
    BreathingStrategy
    This class defines a Breathing Strategy, which grows and shrinks the ball's radius.
    ColorStrategy
    This class defines a Color Strategy, which changes the ball's color.
    CrashStrategy
    This class defines a Crash Strategy which makes the ball change color when it bounces from the boundaries of the canvas.
    EarthImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Earth.
    EllipsePaintStrategy
    This class defines a paint strategy to paint an ellipse shape.
    EllipseShapeFactory
    This class defines a shape factory to make Ellipses.
    FastStrategy
    This class defines a Fast Strategy that makes the ball's velocity increase and stop once it reaches a pre defined max speed.
    HumbirdImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Humbird.
    ImagePaintStrategy
    This class defines a paint strategy for an image that extends APaintStrategy.
    JupiterImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Jupiter.
    MarioImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Mario.
    MarioMarsImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an upright composite shape, a combination of Mars and Mario.
    MarsImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Mars.
    MultiPaintStrategy
    This class defines a multi paint strategy which is the composition of other paint strategies.
    MultiStrategy
    This class defines a Multi Strategy which defines a movement strategy for a ball is a combination of 2 other strategies.
    RectangleEllipsePaintStrategy
    This class defines a composite rectangle ellipse shape that stays upright.
    RectanglePaintStrategy
    This class defines a paint strategy to paint a rectangle shape.
    RectangleShapeFactory
    This class defines a shape factory to make Rectangles.
    ReefImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of a reef.
    SaturnImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of a Saturn.
    ShapePaintStrategy
    This class defines a shape paint strategy.
    SheepImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of a Sheep.
    SoccerImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of a soccer ball.
    SonicImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Sonic.
    SpawnStrategy
    This class defines a spawn strategy that interacts with other balls.
    SquarePaintStrategy
    This is the square paint strategy that paints a square.
    StraightStrategy
    This class defines a Straight Strategy which defines a movement strategy for a ball that just moves by changing it's location by its velocity components.
    SwellStrategy
    This class defines a Swell Strategy which defines a movement strategy for a ball that grows it in size, and once it reaches a certain size, it changes colors, and then shrinks slowly and repeats.
    SwitcherStrategy
    This class defines a Switcher Strategy which defines a strategy for a ball that can change by updating the strategy.
    TeleportStrategy
    This class defines a Teleport Strategy which defines a movement strategy for a ball that randomly changes the location of it, so it teleports.
    UprightImagePaintStrategy
    This class defines an upright image.
    UprightMultiPaintStrategy
    This class defines an upright multi paint strategy composition.
    VenusImagePaintStrategy
    This is the class that paints an image of Venus.
    WiggleStrategy
    This class defines a Wiggle Strategy which defines a movement strategy for a ball that randomly changes the velocity direction, so it wiggles.
